<author>fwạz ʿmysẖ</author>
<title>bḥbh yswʿ qd ạ̉nqdẖny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- biḥubĩhi yasūʿu qad̊ ạản̊qadẖanī
 min̊ ḥam̊ạảẗi ạldẖũnūbi qad̊ rafaʿanī
 (ại̹dẖ̊ kun̊tu fī ạlsẖãrĩ gẖarīqaⁿạ hālikaⁿạ
 bilạ rajā wadar̊bī ạảm̊say̱ ḥālikaⁿạ)2

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: biḥubĩhi fadānī rabĩy
   biḥubĩhi ʿafā ʿan̊ dẖan̊bī
   biḥubĩhi qaḍay̱ biạlṣãl̊bi
   (falạs̊mihi ḥam̊duⁿ mina ạl̊qal̊bi)2

[V2]
 2- biḥubĩhi ʿalay̱ ṣalībi ạl̊jul̊jutẖah̊
 qāsay̱ lạảj̊li naf̊sīa ạl̊mulawãtẖah̊
 (waqad̊ gẖadā ṭarīqī lil̊maj̊di ạl̊ʿatīd̊
 ạảẙḍaⁿạ ḥabānī ạl̊ʿit̊qa wāl̊ʿaf̊wa ạlạảkīd̊)2

[V3]
 3- biḥubĩhi makẖāwifī tabadãdat̊
 raḥ̊matuhu was̊ṭa ạl̊mulimãạti badat̊
 (wah̊wa ạảmāmī fātiḥuⁿ bāba ạlnãʿīm̊
 kaẙ ạảm̊lika maʿ̊hu bimaj̊diⁿ mus̊tadīm̊)2</lyrics>
</song>